    <comment on="column" schema="production" table="billofmaterials" name="unitmeasurecode">Standard code identifying the unit of measure for the quantity.</comment>
    <comment on="column" schema="production" table="billofmaterials" name="bomlevel">Indicates the depth the component is from its parent (AssemblyID).</comment>
    <comment on="column" schema="production" table="billofmaterials" name="perassemblyqty">Quantity of the component needed to create the assembly.</comment>
